comments: Towns (MIN) makes marginal contact with Allen (BKN) during the rebound.
Harris (BKN) cleanly blocks Graham's (MIN) shot attempt near the rim.
Irving (BKN) makes marginal contact to Wiggins' (MIN) body that does not affect his shot attempt.
Teague (MIN) makes contact to Irving's (BKN) body during his shooting motion which affects his jump shot attempt.
LeVert (BKN) briefly places a hand to the opposite side of Towns (MIN) body during the pick but he immediately removes it. The marginal contact does not affect Towns' (MIN) ability to move freely.
Wiggins (MIN) extends his hand into Allen's (BKN) body, warding him off and affecting his ability to contest the driving shot attempt.
Towns (MIN) makes marginal contact to Irving's (BKN) arm during the drive that does not affect his SQBR.
Allen (BKN) establishes himself in a legal screening position in the path of Teague (MIN) when the contact occurs.
Towns (MIN) makes incidental contact with Irving (BKN) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Towns (MIN) makes body and arm contact with Allen (BKN) that affects his play at the basket.
Prince (BKN) briefly grasps Vonleh's (MIN) arm during the rebound but does not dislodge him from his position.
Towns (MIN) cleanly blocks Prince's (BKN) shot attempt near the rim.
Graham (MIN) makes marginal contact with Prince (BKN) that does not affect his play at the basket.
Towns (MIN) jumps vertically and legally contests the drive to the basket by Irving (BKN).
Graham (MIN) grabs and holds Harris (BKN) off ball, affecting his FOM.
Allen (BKN) extends his leg into Graham's (MIN) path and delivers contact during the screen.
Towns (MIN) has his hands placed on Allen's (BKN) back during the rebound, but the contact is marginal.
Towns (MIN) is retreating and absorbs the oncoming contact with Irving (BKN) with a collapsed forearm.
Allen (BKN) initiates contact with Covington (MIN) that affects his ability to control the rebound.
LeVert (BKN) briefly places a hand to the opposite side of Towns (MIN) body during the pick but he immediately removes it.
Covington (MIN) makes contact to Irving's (BKN) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Allen (BKN) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Towns (MIN) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Harris (BKN) makes contact with Wiggins (MIN) while the ball is loose that does not affect his ability to gather it.
Okogie (MIN) makes marginal contact with Irving (BKN) as he falls on his own during his dribble.
